headline.main: No. 10 Stanford Women Beat No. 6 Oregon State to Win Pac-12
headline.print_headline: No. 10 Stanford Women Beat No. 6 Oregon State to Win Pac-12

lead_paragraph: It was only fitting that the season in which coach Tara VanDerveer joined elite company with her 1,000th career win included at least one championship trophy for Stanford.
